title: Concert for Lady Diana Princess of Wales DivX (musicfromrizzo)
description: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0918508/ ON July 1st 2007 a concert was held at Wembley Stadium in London and broadcast live to over 140 countries to commemorate the life of Princess Diana on what would have been her 46th birthday (IMDB comment) Includes comments from Princes William and harry about their dear mother - Lovely Princess Diana Also includes comments from former Prime Minister Bill Blair and others Live performances of great music include those of the great Mr Andrea Bocelli, Bryan Ferry (Slave to love)Rod Stewart Tom Jones Roger Hodgson (Supertramp) Sarah Brightman along with Josh Groban in a duet and Elton John (some performers Id rather not mention as I tend to shun rap music and the like - which I cannot understand for the life of me why was included in this memorable event). Other lesser known artists appear too with their own contributions. 720 X 480 DivX in 2 part files of the concert and one file of supplementary material about concert 1500k video bitrate 192k Dolby stereo audio Converted using DivX author 1.5 from 2 DVD set of the concert. enjoy and please seed Michael Rizzo Chessman - the greatest fan of Lady Diana (musicfromrizzo)
